    <h2 id="howOften">How often should I water?</h2>
    <p>You should provide a plant with thorough watering every few days. Giving the plant plenty of water but watering less frequently is important for growing deep roots. </p>
   
    <!--Need to add in text citations for most of this info.... maybe add a picture-->
